HEADWORD: Zoilean
<hw>Zo*il"e*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having the
characteristic of <ets>Zoilus</ets>, a bitter, envious, unjust critic,
who lived about 270 years before Christ.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

